{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-markdown-page-js","path":"/other/damage","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Shiren SFC Wiki | Zoiteki","docsLocation":"https://github.com/zoiteki/shiren-1/tree/main/content"}},"markdownRemark":{"fields":{"id":"50106126-6909-5f03-a04e-bb9503d0767a","title":"Damage","slug":"/other/damage"},"parent":{"relativePath":"other/damage.md"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Damage","metaTitle":"Damage - Shiren 1 Wiki","metaDescription":"Damage Calculation info for Shiren the Wanderer"},"html":"<h2 id=\"Attack-Formula\" style=\"position:relative;\">Attack Formula<a href=\"#Attack-Formula\" aria-label=\"Attack Formula permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.65 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p>Monsters have a set Attack. Shiren's Attack is based on his Weapon Strength, Strength, and Level.</p>\n<div class=\"math math-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">⌊</mo><mfrac linethickness=\"0.1em\"><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>w</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>s</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>8</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>∗</mo><msub><mi>p</mi><mi>l</mi></msub></mrow><mn>16</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mfrac linethickness=\"0.1em\"><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy=\"false\">⌋</mo><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>p</mi><mi>l</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">a = \\lfloor {(w+s-8)*p_l \\above{1pt} 16} + {1 \\above{1pt} 2} \\rfloor + p_l</annotation></semantics></math></span></div>\n<p><span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>a</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">a</annotation></semantics></math></span></span> = attack<br>\n<span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>w</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">w</annotation></semantics></math></span></span> = weapon strength<br>\n<span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>s</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">s</annotation></semantics></math></span></span> = strength</p>\n<p>Additional information</p>\n<p>Max Attack = 255<br>\nWhen throwing or using arrows: <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>s</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">s=0</annotation></semantics></math></span></span>\r\nIf using Wooden Arrows: <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>w</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">w=5</annotation></semantics></math></span></span><br>\nIf using Iron Arrows: <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>w</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>12</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">w=12</annotation></semantics></math></span></span><br>\nIf using Silver Arrows: <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>w</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>10</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">w=10</annotation></semantics></math></span></span><br>\nWhen throwing a weapon, the strength of the weapon is used as <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>w</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">w</annotation></semantics></math></span></span>\r\nThere is an overflow bug when throwing with a weapon with exceptionally high power</p>\n<ul>\n<li>When: <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>w</mi><mo>≥</mo><mn>136</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">w\\ge136</annotation></semantics></math></span></span>: <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>s</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>256</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">s=-256</annotation></semantics></math></span></span></li>\n<li>Don't throw your +99 Hiken Kaburasutegi!</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>l</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">l</annotation></semantics></math></span></span> = Shiren's Level (Max Level = 70)</p>\n<p><span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>p</mi><mi>l</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">p_l</annotation></semantics></math></span></span> = power array lookup based on Shiren's level. See <a href=\"../experience/\">EXP</a></p>\n<p>(e.g. <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>p</mi><mi>l</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>23</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">p_l = 23</annotation></semantics></math></span></span> when <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>l</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>10</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">l=10</annotation></semantics></math></span></span>)</p>\n<h2 id=\"Damage-Formula\" style=\"position:relative;\">Damage Formula<a href=\"#Damage-Formula\" aria-label=\"Damage Formula permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.65 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<div class=\"math math-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mi>D</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac linethickness=\"0.1em\"><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">⌈</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>∗</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mn>112...144</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo>∗</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mfrac linethickness=\"0.1em\"><mn>15</mn><mn>16</mn></mfrac><msup><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mi>d</mi></msup><mo stretchy=\"false\">⌉</mo></mrow><mn>128</mn></mfrac><mo>∗</mo><mi>m</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">D= {\\lceil a*[112...144]*({15\\above{1pt}16})^d \\rceil\\above{1pt}128}*m</annotation></semantics></math></span></div>\n<p><span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>D</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">D</annotation></semantics></math></span></span> = Damage<br>\n<span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>a</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">a</annotation></semantics></math></span></span> = Attack (see above)<br>\n<span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mn>112...144</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">[112...144]</annotation></semantics></math></span></span> = Random value between 112 &#x26; 144<br>\n<span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>d</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">d</annotation></semantics></math></span></span> = Defense or Shield Strength</p>\n<p>Max Damage is 255</p>\n<p>m is a modifier for crits, weaknesses, and Powerup Scroll.<br>\n<span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>m</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>c</mi><mi>w</mi><mi>P</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">m=cwP</annotation></semantics></math></span></span><br>\nLet c, w, and P = 1<br>\nIf crit: <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">c=2</annotation></semantics></math></span></span><br>\nIf weakness: <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>w</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">w=2</annotation></semantics></math></span></span><br>\nIf Powerup Scroll <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac linethickness=\"0px\"><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P={3\\above{}2}n</annotation></semantics></math></span></span> where n is the number of Powerup scrolls used</p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#attack-formula\">Attack Formula</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#damage-formula\">Damage Formula</a></li>\n</ul>","headings":[{"id":"Attack-Formula","value":"Attack Formula","depth":2},{"id":"Damage-Formula","value":"Damage Formula","depth":2}]},"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/dungeons/feis-final-problem","title":"Feis Final Problem"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/dungeons/food-god","title":"Food God"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/dungeons/scroll-cave","title":"Scroll Cave"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/dungeons","title":"Dungeons"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/","title":"Top Page"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/guides","title":"Guides"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/items","title":"Items"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/other","title":"Other"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/system","title":"System"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/thanks","title":"Credits & Thanks"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/dungeons/table-mountain","title":"Table Mountain"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/guides/basics","title":"Basics"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/guides/blank-scroll-guide","title":"Blank Scroll Guide"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/guides/strategies","title":"Strategies"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/items/arrows","title":"Arrows"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/items/bracers","title":"Bracers"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/items/food","title":"Food"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/items/meat","title":"Meat"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/items/herbs","title":"Herbs"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/items/price-chart","title":"Price Chart"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/items/pots","title":"Pots"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/items/shields","title":"Shields"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/items/staves","title":"Staves"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/items/unidentifieditems","title":"Unidentified Items"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/other/damage","title":"Damage"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/items/scrolls","title":"Scrolls"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/items/weapon